    "strongAgainstReason": "Natan is strong against Tanks with low mobility such as Tigreal and Gatotkaca because he can easily avoid their control abilities with his UIltimate and get more hits in with his Basic Attacks on slower targets.",
    "weakAgainstReason": "Natan is countered by heroes with targeted control and high burst like Saber and Eudora that can lock him down and finish him off.",
    "synergyReason": "Natan's Ultimate allows him to blink a great distance, so he works best with initiator heroes such as Johnson and Alpha because he can dive with them and unleash a lot of damage."
